quran[8{c,v,t}:
7,44,aur ahal bahisht dozakhiyon se pukaar kar kahin ge ke jo wada hamaray perwar-digaar ne hum sekiya tha hum ne to usay sacha pa liya. bhala jo wada tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum sekiya tha tum ne bhi usay sacha paaya? woh kahin ge haan to ( is waqt ) un mein aik pukarnay wala pukare ga ke be insafon par khuda ki laanat
7,45,jo khuda ki raah se roktay aur is mein kajji dhoondtay aur akhirat se inkaar karte they
7,46,un dono ( yani bahisht aur dozakh ) ke darmain ( airaaf naam ) aik deewar ho gi aur airaaf par kuch aadmi hon ge jo sab ko un ki sooraton se pehchan len ge. to woh ahal bahisht ko pukaar kar kahin ge ke tum par salamti ho. yeh log bhi bahisht mein daakhil to nahi hon ge magar umeed rakhtay hon ge
7,47,aur jab un ki nigehain palat kar ahal dozakh ki taraf jayen gi to arz karen ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko zalim logon ke sath shaamil nah kejio
7,48,aur ahal airaaf ( kafir ) logon ko jinhein un ki sooraton se shanakht karte hon ge pukaarain ge aur kahin ge ( ke aaj ) nah to tumhari jamaat hi tumahray kuch kaam aayi aur nah tumhara taqqabur ( hi soodmand howa )
7,49,( phir mominon ki taraf ishara kar ke kahin ge )kiya yeh wohi log hain jin ke baray mein tum kasmain khaya karte they ke khuda apni rehmat se un ki dastgeeri nahi kere ga ( to momino ) tum bahisht mein daakhil ho jao tumhe kuch khauf nahi aur nah tum ko kuch ranj o andoh hoga
7,50,aur woh dozakhi bahishtion se ( girgira kar ) kahin ge ke kisi qader hum par pani bahao ya jo rizaq khuda ne tumhe inayat farmaya hai un mein se ( kuch hamein bhi do ) woh jawab den ge ke khuda ne bahisht ka pani aur rizaq kafiroon par haraam kar diya hai
7,51,jinhon ne apne deen ko tamasha aur khail bana rakha tha aur duniya ki zindagi ne un ko dhokay mein daal rakha tha. to jis terhan yeh log is din ke anay ko bhoolay hue aur hamari ayaton se munhkir ho rahay they. isi terhan aaj hum bhi inhen bhala den ge
